      <title>成本削减促使瑞银升级至买入 UPS 股价两年来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/ups-jumps-most-in-two-years-as-cost-cuts-spur-ubs-upgrade-to-buy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合包裹服务公司(United Parcel Service Inc.)在瑞银集团(UBS Group AG)将快递公司升级为购买评级后创下两年来最大涨幅，并预测该公司在裁减12,000个管理岗位后将继续控制开支。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/ups-jumps-most-in-two-years-as-cost-cuts-spur-ubs-upgrade-to-buy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:52:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
