    <item>
      <title>加拿大央行行长表示利率无法解决高昂的住房成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/bank-of-canada-chief-says-rates-can-t-fix-high-shelter-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行行长蒂夫·麦克勒姆表示，货币政策无法解决导致成本上升的住房短缺问题，这表明政策制定者在权衡将利率维持在当前水平多久时，可能会超越住房通胀问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/bank-of-canada-chief-says-rates-can-t-fix-high-shelter-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
